hopobject.body: Would you like a receipt? ronnie coleman nutrition These are extraordinary times, with extraordinary opportunities. Thanks to human progress, a child born anywhere on Earth today can do things that, 60 years ago, would have been out of reach for the mass of humanity. I saw this in Africa, where nations moving beyond conflict are now poised to take off, and America's with them, partnering to feed the hungry and care for the sick and to bring power to places off the grid.
